text: "Art of Love" is a 2009 song by Australian singer Guy Sebastian featuring Jordin Sparks. It is the second single from his fifth studio album Like It Like That. It went to number 7 in New Zealand and number 8 in Australia. ==Track listing== Sanity: Art Of Love CD. Sanity Music. Archived from the original on 31 January 2012 iTunes: Art Of Love. iTunes.
